        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-10-25 16:13:13.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThe metadata is already supported in the code.\nThe changes proposed break the design of AAIServcie.\n\nAAIService deals with one node at a time, and intentionally does not deal with the whole tree.\nTo achieve what you are looking for you should make a consecutive nodes in the graph.\nFurther explanation of how to write graph data to AAI  is provided in the comments to CCSDK-127 and will be added to how-to wiki.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
